WebAutomation.DataExtraction.ExtractTable BrowserInstance: Browser Control: $'''html > body > div:eq(3) > div > main > div > div:eq(1) > div:eq(0) > div:eq(0) > div > div:eq(1) > div''' ExtractionParameters: {[$'''div:eq(0) > span:eq(0) > p''', $'''Own Text''', $'''''', $'''単位'''], [$'''span:eq(1) > p''', $'''Own Text''', $'''''', $'''円換算'''] } ExtractedData=> DataFromWebPage

@@flowname: 'PADjp_アプリログイン'
External.RunFlow FlowId: 'd656d7a8-911e-4d29-a0c3-31126986c804'
/# ＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊
単位の円換算値を取得し、データを一行ずつ社内アプリに入力
#/
LOOP FOREACH CurrentItem IN ExcelData
    LOOP FOREACH CurrentItem2 IN DataFromWebPage
        IF CurrentItem['単位'] = CurrentItem2['単位'] THEN
            SET EnnKansan TO CurrentItem2['円換算']
            EXIT LOOP
        END
    END
    CALL Tenki
END
